{"tid":2029148,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一名男子涉藉反修例事件眾籌欺詐被捕","createTime":"2020-05-22T06:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T06:16:14.000Z","uid":91771,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"70b03e080881eab7c1ab22fa510b226aa3b3f589","tid":2029148,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:06:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527703-20200522.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527703-20200522.htm&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSiBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=07d2eaaf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527703-20200522.htm&h=8a13352f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527703-20200522.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n警方拘捕一名本地男子涉嫌以眾籌為名欺詐，警方指，男子涉嫌管理一個散播仇恨言論、虛假信息及煽動暴力的社交平台，並經營一個含欺詐成分的網上眾籌平台。<br />\n<br />\n網絡安全及科技罪案調查科警司莫俊傑說，警方本星期三在大埔拘捕這名32歲男子，指他以幫助因反修例事件而流亡海外的人士為名，自去年9月至今成功籌得63萬元。警方懷疑這名男子收取款項後用作其他用途，或將資金轉移至私人戶口。案件仍在調查，不排除會拘捕更多涉案人士。<br />\n<br />\n警方提醒市民必須留意網上眾籌的資金用處，如懷疑被騙，可即時致電警方的反詐騙熱線18222求助。<br />\n<br />\n拉咗大J?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923a47a86244540d8205b4972c42e885f52e4d30","tid":2029148,"uid":50972,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:07:28.000Z","msg":"大j 35,36歲"},{"pid":"fe50cfc9e7c79729ee1d47e6bf6f5a4d0c87c2a7","tid":2029148,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:07:40.000Z","msg":"剛剛嘅新聞"},{"pid":"06afb09f6637686c317422b40d6051a1090e8ffa","tid":2029148,"uid":68689,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:08:00.000Z","msg":"嫌管理一個散播仇恨言論、虛假信息及煽動暴力的社交平台，並經營一個含欺詐成分的網上眾籌平台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868bb19e666e72182d69a7b